snippet.title: Pixel Explosions - Sandboxels
snippet.description:
A look at some of the explosions in our sandbox falling-sand game, Sandboxels.

PLAY IN BROWSER: https://sandboxels.r74n.com/ 

Sandboxels is an in-browser falling sand simulation game, with mechanics such as heat simulation, electricity, density, chemical reactions, fire, and over 300 unique elements to play with.

For game updates, news, and screenshots:
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/ejUc6YPQuS
Follow our Twitter: https://twitter.com/R74nCom

#gamedev #devlog #sandboxels
